# Title: short summary, max 72 characters, imperative mood
# Example: "Add CIS v3.0 to well-known initiative catalogue"
#
# ── What ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# (Optional) Bullet points describing what changed:
#
# -
#
# ── Why ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# (Optional) Why was this change necessary?
#
#
# ── Notes ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Related issue: #
# Breaking change: yes / no
#
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Lines starting with # are ignored by git.
